TRANSFORMATION.DESCRIPTION: Lookup on ITEM table to get ITEM_ID
TRANSFORMATION.NAME: LKP_ITEM

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Lookup Sql Override
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT MIN(ITEM.ITEM_ID) AS ITEM_ID, TRIM(ITEM.SAP_GRID_VALUE) AS SAP_GRID_VALUE, TRIM(ITEM.SAP_MATERIAL_NUM) as SAP_MATERIAL_NUM FROM ITEM WHERE DIVISION_GROUP='slsp' AND ITEM_TYPE_CODE = 'SEL' AND TRIM(ITEM.SAP_MATERIAL_NUM) IS NOT NULL GROUP BY TRIM(ITEM.SAP_GRID_VALUE), TRIM(ITEM.SAP_MATERIAL_NUM)

TRANSFORMATION.DESCRIPTION: Lookup on SAP_ITEM based on the input Style, color, Size, Attribut_cd and get the Material_num and Grid_value. Material_status_code, output either one row.
TRANSFORMATION.NAME: LKP_SAP_ITEM

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Lookup Sql Override
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT MIN(MATERIAL_NUM) AS MATERIAL_NUM, GRID_VALUE AS GRID_VALUE, LEGACY_STYLE AS LEGACY_STYLE,LEGACY_COLOR AS LEGACY_COLOR, LEGACY_SIZE_CODE_SCALE AS LEGACY_SIZE_CODE_SCALE, LEGACY_ATTRIBUTE AS LEGACY_ATTRIBUTE FROM (SELECT MATERIAL_NUM, GRID_VALUE, LEGACY_STYLE, LEGACY_COLOR, LEGACY_SIZE_CODE_SCALE, LEGACY_ATTRIBUTE, RANK() OVER(PARTITION BY LEGACY_STYLE, LEGACY_COLOR, LEGACY_SIZE_CODE_SCALE, LEGACY_ATTRIBUTE ORDER BY CASE WHEN MATERIAL_STATUS_CODE = '50' THEN 1 WHEN MATERIAL_STATUS_CODE > '50' AND MATERIAL_STATUS_CODE < '99' THEN 2 WHEN MATERIAL_STATUS_CODE > '0' AND MATERIAL_STATUS_CODE < '50' THEN 3 ELSE 4 END , CASE WHEN LEGACY_PUTUP_CODE = '000' THEN 1 ELSE 2 END , MATERIAL_NUM ) RNK FROM SAP_ITEM ) WHERE RNK=1 GROUP BY GRID_VALUE, LEGACY_STYLE, LEGACY_COLOR, LEGACY_SIZE_CODE_SCALE, LEGACY_ATTRIBUTE

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Lookup condition
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: LEGACY_STYLE = I_STYLE AND LEGACY_COLOR = I_COLOR AND LEGACY_ATTRIBUTE = I_ATTRIBUTE_CD AND LEGACY_SIZE_CODE_SCALE = I_SIZE_CD

TRANSFORMATION.DESCRIPTION: Source qualifier to get required fields for the CORP_BUSINESS_UNIT in ('PTY', 'BRA')
TRANSFORMATION.NAME: SQ_STG_OW_CORP_PROD_ORDER

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Sql Query
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE:
SELECT A.PROD_ORDER_NO, A.PARENT_PROD_ORDER, TRIM(A.SELLING_STYLE_CD) as SELLING_STYLE_CD, TRIM(A.SELLING_COLOR_CD) as SELLING_COLOR_CD, TRIM(A.SELLING_ATTRIBUTE_CD) as SELLING_ATTRIBUTE_CD , TRIM(A.SELLING_SIZE_CD) as SELLING_SIZE_CD, A.MFG_PLANT, A.NET_ORDER_QTY+A.INTRANSIT_QTY AS NET_ORDER_QTY, A.CURR_DUE_DATE, A.ORIG_DUE_DATE, A.CORP_BUSINESS_UNIT, 'P' AS WIP_IND, A.SCRAP_QTY FROM STAGING.STG_OW_CORP_PROD_ORDER A
where CORP_BUSINESS_UNIT IN ('PTY','BRA') and ORDER_STATUS_CD = '1' and order_source_cd not in ('MITS', 'SAP') AND style_matl_type_cd in ('00','01','02') AND AS_OF_DATE = ( SELECT AS_OF_DATE FROM DAY_DIMENSION WHERE DAY_DATE = TRUNC(SYSDATE) -1 ) and parent_prod_order is not null AND PARENT_PROD_ORDER IN ( SELECT PROD_ORDER_NO FROM STAGING.STG_OW_CORP_PROD_ORDER where parent_prod_order is null AND CORP_BUSINESS_UNIT IN ('PTY','BRA') and order_status_cd = '1' and order_source_cd not in ('MITS', 'SAP') and style_matl_type_cd in ('00','01','02') and as_of_date = ( select as_of_date from day_dimension where day_date = trunc(sysdate) -1 ) )
UNION ALL
SELECT A.PROD_ORDER_NO, A.PARENT_PROD_ORDER, TRIM(A.SELLING_STYLE_CD) as SELLING_STYLE_CD, TRIM(A.SELLING_COLOR_CD) as SELLING_COLOR_CD, TRIM(A.SELLING_ATTRIBUTE_CD) as SELLING_ATTRIBUTE_CD , TRIM(A.SELLING_SIZE_CD) as SELLING_SIZE_CD, A.MFG_PLANT, A.NET_ORDER_QTY+A.INTRANSIT_QTY AS NET_ORDER_QTY, A.CURR_DUE_DATE, A.ORIG_DUE_DATE, A.CORP_BUSINESS_UNIT, case when A.parent_prod_order is not null then 'P' -- when A.PARENT_PROD_ORDER is null then 'U' when A.PARENT_PROD_ORDER is null and create_userid = 'StgETLIssProdOrder' then 'W' else 'U' end as wip_ind , A.SCRAP_QTY FROM staging.STG_OW_CORP_PROD_ORDER A
WHERE CORP_BUSINESS_UNIT IN ('PTY','BRA') AND ORDER_STATUS_CD = '1' and order_source_cd not in ('MITS', 'SAP') AND style_matl_type_cd in ('00','01','02') AND AS_OF_DATE = ( SELECT AS_OF_DATE FROM DAY_DIMENSION WHERE DAY_DATE = TRUNC(SYSDATE) -1 ) AND PARENT_PROD_ORDER IS NULL AND PROD_ORDER_NO NOT IN ( SELECT PARENT_PROD_ORDER FROM STAGING.STG_OW_CORP_PROD_ORDER where parent_prod_order is NOT null AND CORP_BUSINESS_UNIT IN ('PTY','BRA') and order_status_cd = '1' and order_source_cd not in ('MITS', 'SAP') and style_matl_type_cd in ('00','01','02') AND AS_OF_DATE = ( SELECT AS_OF_DATE FROM DAY_DIMENSION where day_date = trunc(sysdate) -1 ) )
UNION ALL
SELECT A.PROD_ORDER_NO, A.PARENT_PROD_ORDER, TRIM(A.SELLING_STYLE_CD) as SELLING_STYLE_CD, TRIM(A.SELLING_COLOR_CD) as SELLING_COLOR_CD, TRIM(A.SELLING_ATTRIBUTE_CD) as SELLING_ATTRIBUTE_CD , TRIM(A.SELLING_SIZE_CD) as SELLING_SIZE_CD, A.MFG_PLANT, A.NET_ORDER_QTY+A.INTRANSIT_QTY AS NET_ORDER_QTY, A.CURR_DUE_DATE, A.ORIG_DUE_DATE, A.CORP_BUSINESS_UNIT, 'P' AS WIP_IND, A.SCRAP_QTY FROM STAGING.STG_OW_CORP_PROD_ORDER A
WHERE CORP_BUSINESS_UNIT IN ('PTY','BRA') AND ORDER_STATUS_CD = '1' and order_source_cd not in ('MITS', 'SAP') AND style_matl_type_cd in ('00','01','02') AND AS_OF_DATE = ( SELECT AS_OF_DATE FROM DAY_DIMENSION WHERE DAY_DATE = TRUNC(SYSDATE) -1 ) AND PARENT_PROD_ORDER IS NULL AND PROD_ORDER_NO IN ( SELECT PARENT_PROD_ORDER FROM STAGING.STG_OW_CORP_PROD_ORDER where parent_prod_order is NOT null AND CORP_BUSINESS_UNIT IN ('PTY','BRA') and style_matl_type_cd in ('00','01','02') and order_status_cd = '1' and order_source_cd not in ('MITS', 'SAP') and as_of_date = ( select as_of_date from day_dimension where day_date = trunc(sysdate) -1 ) )

TRANSFORMATION.DESCRIPTION: Lookup on WIP_INV_STATUS to get required fields.
TRANSFORMATION.NAME: LKP_WIP_INV_STATUS

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Lookup Sql Override
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE:
SELECT WIP_INV_STATUS.INVENTORY_GRP_CD as INVENTORY_GRP_CD, LPAD((WIP_INV_STATUS.INVENTORY_STAT ),2,0) as INVENTORY_STAT FROM
( select INVENTORY_GRP_CD , INVENTORY_STAT from(
select INVENTORY_GRP_CD , INVENTORY_STAT from (select cast(A.INVENTORY_STAT as int) AS INVENTORY_STAT,a.INVENTORY_GRP_CD from wip_inv_status a join wip_inv_grp b on a.INVENTORY_GRP_CD = b.INVENTORY_GRP_CD join wip_inv_grp c on b.INV_PARENT_GRP_CD = c.INVENTORY_GRP_CD where c.inv_parent_grp_cd in ( '200') and b.inv_parent_grp_cd in ( '210') and trim(TRANSLATE(a.INVENTORY_STAT,'+-.0123456789',' ')) is null) where inventory_stat <= 4
UNION ALL
select INVENTORY_GRP_CD , INVENTORY_STAT from (select cast(A.INVENTORY_STAT as int) AS INVENTORY_STAT,a.INVENTORY_GRP_CD from wip_inv_status a join wip_inv_grp b on a.INVENTORY_GRP_CD = b.INVENTORY_GRP_CD join wip_inv_grp c on b.INV_PARENT_GRP_CD = c.INVENTORY_GRP_CD where c.inv_parent_grp_cd in ( '200') and b.inv_parent_grp_cd in ( '220') and trim(TRANSLATE(a.INVENTORY_STAT,'+-.0123456789',' ')) is null) WHERE inventory_stat > 4 and inventory_stat <= 40
UNION aLL
select INVENTORY_GRP_CD , INVENTORY_STAT from (select cast(A.INVENTORY_STAT as int) AS INVENTORY_STAT,a.INVENTORY_GRP_CD from wip_inv_status a join wip_inv_grp b on a.INVENTORY_GRP_CD = b.INVENTORY_GRP_CD join wip_inv_grp c on b.INV_PARENT_GRP_CD = c.INVENTORY_GRP_CD where c.inv_parent_grp_cd in ( '200') and b.inv_parent_grp_cd in ( '240') and trim(TRANSLATE(a.INVENTORY_STAT,'+-.0123456789',' ')) is null) where inventory_stat > 40 ))WIP_INV_STATUS

TRANSFORMATION.DESCRIPTION: Lookup on STG_ISS_CORP_PROD_ORD_ACT
TRANSFORMATION.NAME: LKP_STG_ISS_CORP_PROD_ORD_ACT

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Lookup Sql Override
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE:
SELECT INDICATOR AS INDICATOR, ORDER_NUM AS ORDER_NUM, COMPLETE_DATE AS COMPLETE_DATE FROM ( SELECT 'PROD_ORDER_NO' AS INDICATOR, PROD_ORDER_NO as ORDER_NUM, MAX(COMPLETE_DATE) AS COMPLETE_DATE FROM STAGING.STG_ISS_CORP_PROD_ORD_ACT WHERE ACTIVITY_CD= 'SEW' GROUP BY 'PROD_ORDER_NO', PROD_ORDER_NO
UNION ALL
SELECT 'PARENT_PROD_ORDER' AS INDICATOR, PARENT_PROD_ORDER as ORDER_NUM, COMPLETE_DATE FROM STAGING.STG_ISS_CORP_PROD_ORD_ACT WHERE ACTIVITY_CD= 'SEW')

TRANSFORMATION.DESCRIPTION: This performs lookup on EXTERNAL_SKU_XREF table.
TRANSFORMATION.NAME: LKP_EXTERNAL_SKU_XREF

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Lookup Sql Override
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT TRIM(EXTERNAL_SKU_XREF.EXTERNAL_STYLE) as EXTERNAL_STYLE, TRIM(EXTERNAL_SKU_XREF.EXTERNAL_COLOR) as EXTERNAL_COLOR, TRIM(SUBSTR(EXTERNAL_SKU_XREF.EXTERNAL_SIZE,1,3)) as EXTERNAL_SIZE, CASE WHEN TRIM(EXTERNAL_VERSION)='NOCUP' THEN '' ELSE TRIM(EXTERNAL_VERSION) END as EXTERNAL_VERSION, TRIM(EXTERNAL_SKU_XREF.EXTERNAL_SKU) as EXTERNAL_SKU, TRIM(EXTERNAL_SKU_XREF.STYLE_CD) as STYLE_CD, TRIM(EXTERNAL_SKU_XREF.COLOR_CD) as COLOR_CD, TRIM(EXTERNAL_SKU_XREF.SIZE_CD) as SIZE_CD , TRIM(EXTERNAL_SKU_XREF.ATTRIBUTE_CD) as ATTRIBUTE_CD FROM EXTERNAL_SKU_XREF

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Lookup condition
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: STYLE_CD = I_STYLE_CD AND COLOR_CD = I_COLOR_CD AND SIZE_CD = I_SIZE_CD AND ATTRIBUTE_CD = I_ATTRIBUTE_CD

TRANSFORMATION.DESCRIPTION: Performs lookup on Order_Description table.
TRANSFORMATION.NAME: LKP_ORDER_DESCRIPTION

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Lookup Sql Override
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT ORDER_DESCRIPTION.SCRAP_QTY AS SCRAP_QTY, ORDER_DESCRIPTION.ORDER_LABEL AS ORDER_LABEL FROM (select a.order_label, max(a.scrap_factor) + sum(nvl(b.scrap_factor,0)) as Scrap_Qty from order_description a , order_description b where a.order_label = b.note(+) GROUP BY a.order_label) ORDER_DESCRIPTION --

TRANSFORMATION.NAME: LKP_DAY_DIMENSION

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Lookup Sql Override
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT DAY_DIMENSION.AS_OF_DATE as AS_OF_DATE, 'X' as DUMMY FROM DAY_DIMENSION WHERE DAY_DIMENSION.DAY_DATE=TRUNC(SYSDATE)-1

TRANSFORMATION.DESCRIPTION: Expression to calculate field values.
TRANSFORMATION.NAME: EXP_SETVAL

TRANSFORMFIELD.EXPRESSION: IIF(WIP_TYPE_IND<>'W', IIF( NOT ISNULL(PARENT_PROD_ORDER), PARENT_PROD_ORDER, PROD_ORDER_NO), PROD_ORDER_NO)
TRANSFORMFIELD.NAME: O_ORDER_NUM

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Lookup condition
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: STYLE_CD = I_STYLE_CD AND COLOR_CD = I_COLOR_CD AND SIZE_CD = I_SIZE_CD AND ATTRIBUTE_CD = I_ATTRIBUTE_CD
